structure.unit: GENERAL PROVISIONS AS TO OFFICES AND OFFICERS -- SOCIAL SECURITY FOR PUBLIC EMPLOYEES -- EMPLOYEES RETIREMENT SYSTEM

law.history: Repealed 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 42, sec. 29. -- Amended 1944 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 3747a-1, 3747a-2.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Local officers to make annual statement of collections and disbursements; publication; penalty for failure; publication of list of delinquent taxpayers; when legal publications to be in newspaper with largest bona fide circulation.
